https://help.ubuntu.com/12.04/serverguide/mysql.html

===Server===
1) is server running
	=<sudo netstat -tap | grep mysql
	=>tcp        0      0 localhost:mysql         *:*                LISTEN      2556/mysql
2) restart
	=<sudo service mysql restart
3) config file
	/etc/mysql/my.cnf
4) change root password
	=<sudo dpkg-reconfigure mysql-server-5.5

===Client===
1) mysql -u root -p
2) show databases;
3) use database;
4) show tables;
5) select * from table;

